&lt;a href="https://gist.github.com/gaborcsardi/68960fb01bec74d89611bb9c2b0b7e5a">walk-through&lt;/a>
by &lt;a href="https://github.com/gaborcsardi">Gábor Csárdi&lt;/a>&lt;sup id="fnref:2">&lt;a href="#fn:2" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref">2&lt;/a>&lt;/sup>. I used it and it worked
well for a while, but at some point I had an issue with the deployment part
(still not sure why), so I changed it. Instead of using the following
config&lt;sup id="fnref:3">&lt;a href="#fn:3" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref">3&lt;/a>&lt;/sup>&lt;/p>
